## MCP Transport

This CLI contains MCP commands generated from `streamable_http` servers.

- Generation-time discovery used `initialize` and `tools/list`
- Runtime tool execution uses `tools/call`
- Override the generated endpoint with `OPENCLI_BASE_URL` when needed

```bash
export OPENCLI_BASE_URL='http://127.0.0.1:8000/mcp'
```
{{- end }}

